==English==
===Pronunciation===
[[w:General American|GenAm]] {{IPA|[&#712;ka&#618;&#716;b&#593;&#643;]}}, {{IPA|[ka&#618;&#712;b&#593;&#643;]}}, or {{IPA|[k&#618;&#712;b&#593;&#643;]}}

===Etymology===
From the [[w:Irish language|Irish]] ''[[caidhp bháis]],'' meaning ''[[death cap]]'' (the [[hood]] put on [[someone]] before they were [[hang|hanged]] to death).

OR

From the [[w:Scots language|Scots]] ''[[kye booties]],'' meaning ''[[cow boots]]'' (the [[hobble]] put on [[cattle]] to prevent them from straying).

OR

From the [[w:Hebrew language|Hebrew]] ''[[כבש]],'' ''kbsh'' meaning ''[[conquer]]'' ''[[press down]]''

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}
#A [[check|checking]] or [[restrain|restraining]] [[element]].

